      "Architect owns candidate generation, selection, and decision records before CE closure.",
      "The Kernel already defines an Architect source/card consumption boundary, making this the smallest compatible extension.",
      "Requiring Kernel refs at the Architect output boundary prevents silent free decisions for resolver-covered families without modifying multiple repositories."
    ]
  },
  "schema_ref": "kernel/schemas/downstream-consumer-contract.v0.schema.json",
